      "type": "feat",
      "img": "modules/naruto-d20/icons/feat-chakra-reserve.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>At 2nd level, a shinobi develops a <b>Chakra Reserve</b> — a deeper well of spiritual energy equal to their character level + Constitution modifier (minimum 1). The Reserve cannot be spent directly; instead, a shinobi can transfer chakra from the Reserve to the Pool as a standard action (1 point per action) or as a full-round action to transfer all remaining Reserve points at once.</p>"
        },
